headline.main: Senate to Consider Repeal of Obama-Era Labor Rule
headline.print_headline: Senate to Consider Repeal of Obama-Era Labor Rule

lead_paragraph: The new restriction will apply to citizens of six predominately Muslim nations in an effort to improve on a hastily drawn order in January that did not pass legal scrutiny.
